THE kasi auction is the place to go to get the things you want at the right price. The community of Joko Tea squatter camp in Lethabong, Vaal, south of Joburg, realised some residents were in desperate need of things other residents no longer needed.So the kasi people decided to host an auction, which they now want to run every few weeks.if(typeof za24_DisplayAd != "undefined") za24_DisplayAd("300x250","2");var viewReq = new Array();function vu(u) {var i=new Image();i.src=u.replace("&amp;","&");viewReq.push(i);}vu("https://securepubads.g.doubleclick.net/pcs/view?xai\x3dAKAOjsvywtAR6SpsXLAPJE8HKGzN-HygAPfjmKSlpKCE_xzWrgW92C4x2Oh2Qg-Cy6jhxYcOtjOhMcGky2GHglS2WzmLYz9UcI_pcQh3zRb7C2zkD8oRX6DFuCU-L0tsmCYhD9ywZcISjgZzmSBmd5k1enbR6Z27vKFDjqdGGKEEsex8SfSk931DR6B158osr0r2kdbqFuc57lRwSB6t6w-A3vyqJC4Jyc97drSMVVzl9ggqd6eM2iq_aviWYypiw6oRzGzjXQEsCX_4fG0MsBWLqgObYxYLACY\x26sig\x3dCg0ArKJSzP5U9Y73wOmaEAE\x26urlfix\x3d1\x26adurl\x3d")

   
